    "panels": [
      {
        "text": "### Nested Loops\n\nSome songs have unique patterns that you want to repeat throughout the song, like these 3 beats and an effect.\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/72b0396662e7c1b0052c3c0c443b56c4-Slide30.PNG",
        "key": "test-music-lab-loops-practice-panel-nested-loops-6424dfa1-c1a5-4db6-838f-446192842793",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "### Nested Loops\n\nYou can place this entire pattern in its own loop to keep repeating it\n\nThis is called **nesting loops** because one loop is inside the other.\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/3c91189d132236f4ec0054366aed06f4-Slide31.PNG",
        "key": "test-music-lab-loops-practice-panel-nested-loops-6e88ac7b-d408-4cbd-b77a-b771be32870b",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "### Nested Loops\n\nThe original pattern is still in the timeline\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/9c97a93cbb390163ab6bfca5cca574bb-Slide32.PNG",
        "key": "test-music-lab-loops-practice-panel-nested-loops-48c38a70-183f-4953-8179-f0ed30f937d2",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "### Nested Loops\n\nAnd is repeated 2 times\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/012562f7be005144204df4b7f51da8b6-Slide33.PNG",
        "key": "test-music-lab-loops-practice-panel-nested-loops-1eb8f911-42b9-4e31-866b-f1265a080959",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "### Nested Loops\n\nThis can be useful when you've made a pattern you like with different lengths\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/294e951648702c56e16f74823eef11de-Slide34.PNG",
        "key": "test-music-lab-loops-practice-panel-nested-loops-d85ee4e8-acdc-48b0-86cf-a9c19081f7c7",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "### Nested Loops\n\nAnd you want to repeat it throughout the song\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/d9177b8ad7ba27da9e004e439b94dfc0-Slide35.PNG",
        "key": "test-music-lab-loops-practice-panel-nested-loops-bdda94a3-26ee-4978-8040-de86fb1258c9",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "Key Takeaway: You can make patterns with loops. You can repeat those patterns by nesting loops, which means putting your loops inside other loops.",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/78a1bdd2358a7815c0156f1da59cb045-Slide36.PNG",
        "key": "test-music-lab-loops-practice-panel-nested-loops-d31c1347-04e3-43f7-8131-078004cc7b98",
        "typing": true,
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      }
    ],
